This paper discusses the role of tag suggestions in collaborative tagging systems, which is a topic related to social tagging, information retrieval, human-computer interaction, and computational linguistics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
